### GET /api/v1/admin/ops/payments
### Descripción: Listar pagos con filtros. Requiere rol Admin o Support.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>
### Query: tenantId?, status?, from?, to?, tripId?
### Códigos: 200 OK (lista PaymentOpsDto)

# @name getPaymentsOps
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/ops/payments?tenantId={{TENANT_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}

### Response esperado (200):
# [
#   { "id", "tenantId", "tripId", "payerId", "amount", "currency", "status", "externalPaymentId", "createdAtUtc" }
# ]

### Response error: 401 si no autenticado
